{"word":"G1987 - ἐπίσταμαι - epístamai - ep-is'-tam-ahee - Know","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπίσταμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epístamai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-is'-tam-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Know</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அறிந்திரு, தெரிந்திரு, அறி"},{"paragraph":"to know, to be acquainted with"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently a middle voice of <a href=\"#/G2186 - ἐφίστημι - ephístēmi - ef-is'-tay-mee/2186\">G2186</a> (with <a href=\"#/G3563 - νοῦς - noûs - nooce/3563\">G3563</a> implied); to <i>put</i> the mind <i>upon</i>, that is, <i>comprehend</i>, or <i>be acquainted with:</i> - know, understand.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}